415
00:15:13,250 --> 00:15:14,666
[SAIKI]
That's quite the dramatic name.

416
00:15:14,750 --> 00:15:16,625
[KAIDOU] It's also likely
that Dark Reunion genetically

417
00:15:16,708 --> 00:15:19,458
