specifically to kill people!

418
00:15:19,541 --> 00:15:20,583
[SAIKI]
He's fond of saying "likely."

419
00:15:20,666 --> 00:15:22,416
We're running out
of time here, Saiki.

420
00:15:22,500 --> 00:15:24,041
the world's counting on us
to stop that slithering--

421
00:15:24,125 --> 00:15:25,791
Hey! Good news,
they caught the snake.

422
00:15:25,875 --> 00:15:27,500
Well, that's a relief.
Where did they find it?

423
00:15:27,583 --> 00:15:29,166
[BOY STUDENT M]
At the school's front gate!

424
00:15:29,250 --> 00:15:31,458
It was just kinda laying
on the ground, half-dead.

425
00:15:31,541 --> 00:15:32,833
[KAIDOU]
Is it possible Saiki and I 

426
00:15:32,916 --> 00:15:34,541
aren't the only students
with superpowers?

427
00:15:34,625 --> 00:15:36,000
[GIRL STUDENT G]
'Kay, why was it half-dead?

428
00:15:36,083 --> 00:15:37,333
[BOY STUDENT M]
Some first graders had been

429
00:15:37,416 --> 00:15:38,416
whipping it around.

430
00:15:38,500 --> 00:15:40,125
[SAIKI]
That's one weakass murder-snake.

431
00:15:40,208 --> 00:15:42,125
Sounds like we beat
Dark Reunion this time.

432
00:15:42,208 --> 00:15:43,208
Be careful what you say!

433
00:15:43,291 --> 00:15:45,041
They're an all-powerful
secret society.

434
00:15:45,125 --> 00:15:46,541
[GIRL STUDENT H]
Who knows what they'll do to you

435
00:15:46,625 --> 00:15:47,916
when they "sort mankind"!

436
00:15:48,000 --> 00:15:49,291
[STUDENTS laughing]

437
00:15:49,375 --> 00:15:52,166
Hah. Go ahead and laugh!

438
00:15:52,250 --> 00:15:54,041
This is the calm
before the storm.

439
00:15:54,125 --> 00:15:56,250
Dark Reunion is coming.

440
00:15:56,333 --> 00:15:57,916
I tried to warn
you all, I swear.

441
00:15:58,000 --> 00:16:00,208
[SAIKI] He's going
to the bathroom to cry.

442
00:16:00,291 --> 00:16:01,625
Whoa. I'd better go with him.

443
00:16:01,708 --> 00:16:02,875
[BOY STUDENT N]
...pretends he's a super hero!

444
00:16:02,958 --> 00:16:04,208
It's like he's in
elementary school!

445
00:16:04,291 --> 00:16:06,041
One time, he said there's
a monster in his arm!

446
00:16:06,125 --> 00:16:07,375
[BOY STUDENT N gags]

447
00:16:07,458 --> 00:16:08,916
You guys, it's starting to
take over my whole body!

448
00:16:09,000 --> 00:16:09,916
[BOY STUDENT P laughs]

449
00:16:10,000 --> 00:16:10,750
Watch out!

450
00:16:10,833 --> 00:16:12,541
There's something in there!

451
00:16:12,625 --> 00:16:13,416
[STUDENTS gasp]

452
00:16:13,500 --> 00:16:15,250
[BOY STUDENT P]
Ah! Snake!

453
00:16:15,333 --> 00:16:16,333
[BOY STUDENT Q]
Get out!

454
00:16:16,416 --> 00:16:17,291
[BOY STUDENT R]
It's blocking the door!

455
00:16:17,375 --> 00:16:18,791
[SAIKI]
I saw that snake coming.

456
00:16:18,875 --> 00:16:21,208
Y'know, because I'm psychic.

457
00:16:21,291 --> 00:16:23,166
I could help them,
but I'd have to out myself.

458
00:16:23,250 --> 00:16:25,583
So, I'll just stay here
until things calm down.

459
00:16:25,666 --> 00:16:26,916
Speaking of calming down,

460
00:16:27,000 --> 00:16:29,250
Kaidou should stay
here for a while, too.

461
00:16:29,333 --> 00:16:30,708
Now, back to that snake attack.

462
00:16:30,791 --> 00:16:32,166
[BOY STUDENT S]
